        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Court Legal Access and Student Support Act of </b><strong>2021</strong><strong> or the CLASS Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits institutions of higher education (IHEs) that participate in federal student-aid programs from restricting students' ability to pursue claims against IHEs in court. In addition, the bill makes mandatory arbitration agreements inapplicable to enrollment agreements between students and IHEs.]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
